library(tidyverse)
library(textdata)
library(tidytext)
library(janeaustenr)
phrases <- c(
  "Here is some text.",
  "Again more text",
  "TEXT is text?"
)

example_text <- tibble(phrase = phrases,
                       id = seq_along(phrases))

example_text %>% 
    unnest_tokens(word, phrase)
lines_df %>% 
  group_by(word) %>% 
  summarise(count = n()) %>% 
  filter(count > 1)
